sCellEventTrap_01_02.name: sCellEventTrap_01_02
sCellEventTrap_01_02.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A time change occurred.

sCellEventTrap_03_00.name: sCellEventTrap_03_00
sCellEventTrap_03_00.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. An HSV210 controller has failed in communicating with the Cabinet (Rack) Bus Interface Controller.

sCellEventTrap_03_01.name: sCellEventTrap_03_01
sCellEventTrap_03_01.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A physical disk drive has been rendered inoperable.

sCellEventTrap_03_02.name: sCellEventTrap_03_02
sCellEventTrap_03_02.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. A physical disk drive will not be used because the maximum number of physical disk drives already exist in the current Storage System.

sCellEventTrap_03_03.name: sCellEventTrap_03_03
sCellEventTrap_03_03.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller has begun booting.

sCellEventTrap_03_04.name: sCellEventTrap_03_04
sCellEventTrap_03_04.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller has finished the process of bringing the Storage System online.

sCellEventTrap_03_05.name: sCellEventTrap_03_05
sCellEventTrap_03_05.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller has been joined into the Storage System.

sCellEventTrap_03_06.name: sCellEventTrap_03_06
sCellEventTrap_03_06.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller has been ousted from the Storage System.

sCellEventTrap_03_07.name: sCellEventTrap_03_07
sCellEventTrap_03_07.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller is now the Storage System Master.

sCellEventTrap_03_08.name: sCellEventTrap_03_08
sCellEventTrap_03_08.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller has been brought into the Storage System.

sCellEventTrap_03_09.name: sCellEventTrap_03_09
sCellEventTrap_03_09.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The Redundant Storage Set identified in the source-rss field has started migrating members to the Redundant Storage Set identified in the target-rss field.

sCellEventTrap_03_0a.name: sCellEventTrap_03_0a
sCellEventTrap_03_0a.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The Redundant Storage Set identified in the source-rss field has finished migrating members to the Redundant Storage Set identified in the target-rss field.

sCellEventTrap_03_0b.name: sCellEventTrap_03_0b
sCellEventTrap_03_0b.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. A physical disk drive has failed during Storage System realization.

sCellEventTrap_04_00.name: sCellEventTrap_04_00
sCellEventTrap_04_00.description: Severity: Undetermined -- more information needed to determine severity. HSV210 controller operation was terminated due to an unrecoverable event detected by either software or hardware or due to an action initiated via the Storage System Management Interface.

sCellEventTrap_04_01.name: sCellEventTrap_04_01
sCellEventTrap_04_01.description: Severity: Undetermined -- more information needed to determine severity. This HSV210 controller has received a last gasp message from another HSV210 controller prior to it terminating operation.

sCellEventTrap_04_02.name: sCellEventTrap_04_02
sCellEventTrap_04_02.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A machine check occurred while a termination event was being processed.

sCellEventTrap_04_03.name: sCellEventTrap_04_03
sCellEventTrap_04_03.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. An unexpected event occurred while a termination event was being processed.

sCellEventTrap_04_04.name: sCellEventTrap_04_04
sCellEventTrap_04_04.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The Storage System Event Log validation completed successfully.

sCellEventTrap_04_05.name: sCellEventTrap_04_05
sCellEventTrap_04_05.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The Storage System Event Log validation failed.

sCellEventTrap_04_06.name: sCellEventTrap_04_06
sCellEventTrap_04_06.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. Local event reports were lost due to an insufficient supply of Event Log Packets on this HSV210 controller.

sCellEventTrap_04_07.name: sCellEventTrap_04_07
sCellEventTrap_04_07.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. Remote event reports were lost due to an insufficient supply of Event Log Packets on this HSV210 controller.

sCellEventTrap_04_08.name: sCellEventTrap_04_08
sCellEventTrap_04_08.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The Storage System Termination Event Log has become inaccessible.

sCellEventTrap_04_09.name: sCellEventTrap_04_09
sCellEventTrap_04_09.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The Storage System Termination Event Log validation completed successfully.

sCellEventTrap_04_0a.name: sCellEventTrap_04_0a
sCellEventTrap_04_0a.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The Storage System Termination Event Log validation failed.

sCellEventTrap_04_0b.name: sCellEventTrap_04_0b
sCellEventTrap_04_0b.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The Storage System Termination Event Log has been updated with the termination event information obtained from the HSV210 controller that is not the Storage System Master.

sCellEventTrap_04_0c.name: sCellEventTrap_04_0c
sCellEventTrap_04_0c.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The Fault Manager on the Storage System Master received an invalid Event Information Packet from the remote Fault Manager.

sCellEventTrap_04_0d.name: sCellEventTrap_04_0d
sCellEventTrap_04_0d.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The Fault Manager operation was made quiescent.

sCellEventTrap_04_0e.name: sCellEventTrap_04_0e
sCellEventTrap_04_0e.description: Severity: Undetermined -- more information needed to determine severity. An HSV210 controller sent a last gasp message prior to terminating operation with an indication that both HSV210 controllers should terminate operation.

sCellEventTrap_04_0f.name: sCellEventTrap_04_0f
sCellEventTrap_04_0f.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. This HSV210 controller sent its termination event information to the HSV210 controller that is the Storage System Master.

sCellEventTrap_04_10.name: sCellEventTrap_04_10
sCellEventTrap_04_10.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. Event reports were lost due to an insufficient supply of ISR Event Log Packets on the HSV210 controller that is the Storage System Master.

sCellEventTrap_04_11.name: sCellEventTrap_04_11
sCellEventTrap_04_11.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. Event reports were lost due to an insufficient supply of ISR Event Log Packets on the HSV210 controller that is not the Storage System Master.

sCellEventTrap_04_12.name: sCellEventTrap_04_12
sCellEventTrap_04_12.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The last event reporting interval has changed or last event reporting has been enabled or disabled.

sCellEventTrap_04_13.name: sCellEventTrap_04_13
sCellEventTrap_04_13.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. Storage System event reporting is still active.

sCellEventTrap_06_00.name: sCellEventTrap_06_00
sCellEventTrap_06_00.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A physical disk drive has reported that it has exceeded its failure prediction threshold.

sCellEventTrap_06_01.name: sCellEventTrap_06_01
sCellEventTrap_06_01.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. A Fibre Channel port on the HSV210 controller has failed to respond.

sCellEventTrap_06_02.name: sCellEventTrap_06_02
sCellEventTrap_06_02.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A physical disk drive has reported a check condition error.

sCellEventTrap_06_03.name: sCellEventTrap_06_03
sCellEventTrap_06_03.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. An exchange sent to a physical disk drive or another HSV210 controller via the mirror port or a Fibre Channel port has timed out.

sCellEventTrap_06_04.name: sCellEventTrap_06_04
sCellEventTrap_06_04.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. Work was unexpectedly sent to this HSV210 controller by a physical disk drive or another HSV210 controller.

sCellEventTrap_06_05.name: sCellEventTrap_06_05
sCellEventTrap_06_05.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. Work has been sent to a physical disk drive or another HSV210 controller via the mirror port but it did not respond.

sCellEventTrap_06_07.name: sCellEventTrap_06_07
sCellEventTrap_06_07.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. A Target Discovery Service Descriptor exchange sent to a physical disk drive has timed out.

sCellEventTrap_06_08.name: sCellEventTrap_06_08
sCellEventTrap_06_08.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An excessive number of link errors were detected on a HSV210 controller's Fibre Channel port. This informational event is triggered by the occurrence of an excessive number of Tachyon chip link status errors detected within a particular link status error type.

sCellEventTrap_06_09.name: sCellEventTrap_06_09
sCellEventTrap_06_09.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A physical disk drive has reported numerous failure prediction threshold exceeded errors.

sCellEventTrap_06_0a.name: sCellEventTrap_06_0a
sCellEventTrap_06_0a.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A physical disk drive has reported numerous check condition errors.

sCellEventTrap_06_0b.name: sCellEventTrap_06_0b
sCellEventTrap_06_0b.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. A non-data exchange sent to a physical disk drive has timed out.

sCellEventTrap_06_0c.name: sCellEventTrap_06_0c
sCellEventTrap_06_0c.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A loop switch has been detected on a Fibre Channel port.

sCellEventTrap_06_0d.name: sCellEventTrap_06_0d
sCellEventTrap_06_0d.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The location of a physical disk drive previously reported as unknown is now known.

sCellEventTrap_06_0e.name: sCellEventTrap_06_0e
sCellEventTrap_06_0e.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit requested a code update but the code update could not be found, so the update was not performed.

sCellEventTrap_06_0f.name: sCellEventTrap_06_0f
sCellEventTrap_06_0f.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. The Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit is able to communicate with a physical disk drive but this HSV210 controller is unable to communicate with that physical disk drive on the Fibre Channel bus.

sCellEventTrap_06_10.name: sCellEventTrap_06_10
sCellEventTrap_06_10.description: Severity: Undetermined -- more information needed to determine severity. An HSV210 controller is unable to communicate with this Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit.

sCellEventTrap_06_12.name: sCellEventTrap_06_12
sCellEventTrap_06_12.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The retry count for a task assigned to a Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit has been exhausted.

sCellEventTrap_06_13.name: sCellEventTrap_06_13
sCellEventTrap_06_13.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit is able to communicate with this HSV210 controller.

sCellEventTrap_06_14.name: sCellEventTrap_06_14
sCellEventTrap_06_14.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. There are too many drive enclosures attached to a Fibre Channel port.

sCellEventTrap_06_15.name: sCellEventTrap_06_15
sCellEventTrap_06_15.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. The cable connected to the I/O module is attached to the wrong Fibre Channel port.

sCellEventTrap_06_16.name: sCellEventTrap_06_16
sCellEventTrap_06_16.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. An HSV210 controller does not have an address on the enclosure address bus.

sCellEventTrap_06_18.name: sCellEventTrap_06_18
sCellEventTrap_06_18.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit has begun updating its code. Do not power down this drive enclosure until the code update has completed.

sCellEventTrap_06_19.name: sCellEventTrap_06_19
sCellEventTrap_06_19.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit has completed updating its code. It is now safe to power down this drive enclosure.

sCellEventTrap_06_1a.name: sCellEventTrap_06_1a
sCellEventTrap_06_1a.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A physical disk drive has exceeded its soft error threshold.

sCellEventTrap_06_1b.name: sCellEventTrap_06_1b
sCellEventTrap_06_1b.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller now has an address on the enclosure address bus.

sCellEventTrap_06_1c.name: sCellEventTrap_06_1c
sCellEventTrap_06_1c.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. An outbound frame targeted to a physical disk drive has timed out.

sCellEventTrap_06_1d.name: sCellEventTrap_06_1d
sCellEventTrap_06_1d.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. A Fibre Channel exchange to a physical disk drive has completed but is missing data.

sCellEventTrap_06_1e.name: sCellEventTrap_06_1e
sCellEventTrap_06_1e.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. An HSV210 controller has detected only one port of a Fibre Channel device.

sCellEventTrap_06_1f.name: sCellEventTrap_06_1f
sCellEventTrap_06_1f.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A previously reported Fibre Channel device with only one port has been corrected and redundancy has been restored.

sCellEventTrap_06_20.name: sCellEventTrap_06_20
sCellEventTrap_06_20.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. An unsupported Fibre Channel device has been detected. The device has been failed to prevent possible data corruption or system instability.

sCellEventTrap_06_21.name: sCellEventTrap_06_21
sCellEventTrap_06_21.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A Fibre Channel device with incorrect block size has been detected.

sCellEventTrap_06_23.name: sCellEventTrap_06_23
sCellEventTrap_06_23.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller is about to retry a failed port.

sCellEventTrap_06_24.name: sCellEventTrap_06_24
sCellEventTrap_06_24.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller has successfully retried a failed port.

sCellEventTrap_06_25.name: sCellEventTrap_06_25
sCellEventTrap_06_25.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit has failed to assign a hard address to a physical disk drive on the loop.

sCellEventTrap_06_26.name: sCellEventTrap_06_26
sCellEventTrap_06_26.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit has failed to assign an address to a physical disk drive on the loop. This has occurred because another physical disk drive has already obtained this AL-PA.

sCellEventTrap_06_27.name: sCellEventTrap_06_27
sCellEventTrap_06_27.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit has failed to assign address(s) to a physical disk drive on the loop. Soft addressing was detected for this enclosure.

sCellEventTrap_06_28.name: sCellEventTrap_06_28
sCellEventTrap_06_28.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The retry count for an OB task assigned to a Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit has been exhausted.

sCellEventTrap_06_29.name: sCellEventTrap_06_29
sCellEventTrap_06_29.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The HSV210 controller has sent a Basic Link Service command Abort Sequence Frame.

sCellEventTrap_06_2a.name: sCellEventTrap_06_2a
sCellEventTrap_06_2a.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The HSV210 controller has sent an Extended Link Service command Reinstate Recovery Qualifier.

sCellEventTrap_06_2b.name: sCellEventTrap_06_2b
sCellEventTrap_06_2b.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A physical disk drive was bypassed rendering it unusable.

sCellEventTrap_06_2c.name: sCellEventTrap_06_2c
sCellEventTrap_06_2c.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. One or more media defects were detected on a physical disk drive.

sCellEventTrap_06_2d.name: sCellEventTrap_06_2d
sCellEventTrap_06_2d.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller issued a directed LIP to an arbitrated loop physical address.

sCellEventTrap_06_2e.name: sCellEventTrap_06_2e
sCellEventTrap_06_2e.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller has detected loop receiver failures.

sCellEventTrap_06_30.name: sCellEventTrap_06_30
sCellEventTrap_06_30.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. An HSV210 controller has detected only one port of all Fibre Channel devices in an enclosure.

sCellEventTrap_06_31.name: sCellEventTrap_06_31
sCellEventTrap_06_31.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A previously reported Fibre Channel device enclosure with only one port has been corrected and redundancy has been restored.

sCellEventTrap_06_32.name: sCellEventTrap_06_32
sCellEventTrap_06_32.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. An HSV210 controller has detected only one port of all Fibre Channel devices on a loop.

sCellEventTrap_06_33.name: sCellEventTrap_06_33
sCellEventTrap_06_33.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A previously reported Fibre Channel loop with only one port has been corrected and redundancy has been restored.

sCellEventTrap_06_34.name: sCellEventTrap_06_34
sCellEventTrap_06_34.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. An HSV210 controller has been told to enable a device port, and that device port was not disabled during boot diagnostics.

sCellEventTrap_06_35.name: sCellEventTrap_06_35
sCellEventTrap_06_35.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. An unrecognized Fibre Channel physical disk drive firmware revision has been detected by the physical disk drive firmware load process.

sCellEventTrap_06_36.name: sCellEventTrap_06_36
sCellEventTrap_06_36.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. An unsupported Fibre Channel physical disk drive firmware revision has been detected by the physical disk drive firmware load process.

sCellEventTrap_06_37.name: sCellEventTrap_06_37
sCellEventTrap_06_37.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A Fibre Channel physical disk drive firmware revision has been detected by the physical disk drive firmware load process that is later than the latest known supported revision.

sCellEventTrap_06_38.name: sCellEventTrap_06_38
sCellEventTrap_06_38.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A Fibre Channel physical disk drive firmware revision has been detected by the physical disk drive firmware load process that has a newer supported revision available.

sCellEventTrap_06_39.name: sCellEventTrap_06_39
sCellEventTrap_06_39.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The HSV210 controller bypassed a device bay in an attempt to restore operability.

sCellEventTrap_06_3a.name: sCellEventTrap_06_3a
sCellEventTrap_06_3a.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The HSV210 controller is attempting to recovery devices on the indicated port.

sCellEventTrap_06_3b.name: sCellEventTrap_06_3b
sCellEventTrap_06_3b.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The HSV210 controller has finished error recovery attempts on the indicated port.

sCellEventTrap_06_3c.name: sCellEventTrap_06_3c
sCellEventTrap_06_3c.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The HSV210 controller been requested to unbypass device bays on the indicated port.

sCellEventTrap_06_3d.name: sCellEventTrap_06_3d
sCellEventTrap_06_3d.description: Severity: Undetermined -- more information needed to determine severity. The HSV210 controller has detected a enclosure on the enclosure address bus that does not have a Fibre Channel connection.

sCellEventTrap_06_3e.name: sCellEventTrap_06_3e
sCellEventTrap_06_3e.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. The HSV210 controller has detected an enclosure on the Fibre Channel but is unable to communicate with the Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit on the enclosure address bus or the Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit is reporting an invalid enclosure number.

sCellEventTrap_06_3f.name: sCellEventTrap_06_3f
sCellEventTrap_06_3f.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. A physical disk drive is using an improper protocol to attempt communication with an Drive Enclosure Environmental Monitoring Unit. The physical disk drive identified in the device field has stopped communicating with the HSV210 controller.
